Description:

The program gets file name of a picture in PGM format and separates the pictures into segments by threshold that the user input.
The program saves the colored image in a compressed format and converts the compressed image to PGM picture.
The user has a option to choose from the following options:

* insert picture file name in PGM format.
* find all gray color segment. 
* save the colored image in a compressed format.
* insert a picture file name, compress and save the original image in a compressed format.
* convert a compressed image to PGM format in a file.
